143
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:35,320
You don't need to say goodbye
to anyone here.

144
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,520
An Chuxia,

145
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:39,880
I'm sorry.

146
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:43,200
It doesn't matter, Miss Xiang.

147
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,080
Now,

148
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,880
I've started to envy you.

149
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:51,880
Qi...

150
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,320
Han Qilu,

151
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,560
I'm going abroad.

152
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,640
I wish you happy.

153
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:01,240
Thanks.

154
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:11,960
